	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			To get the Iron Pike you have to first secure the tower in Mistmoore castle. This can be easily done with a good group by first going through the Grave Yard then through the secret wall on the left side of the crypt. Once inside you will be in the &quot;bug room&quot;, clear ity if there are casters in there. Then go through the second secret wall and you will see stairs going up. Go up the stairs and clear the two casters that usually guard it. When you reach the top you will see a wooden door on the left and a catwalk leading to the tower on the right. Go right across the catwalk. Keep in mind that the casters in the tower DO NOT have line of sight and can bombard you as you try to clear the the first level of the tower. Try to use a druid to pull the monsters individually. Once the first level is cleared, inside the tower you will see a wooden platform. Click on it and it will lower. Get your group to hop on and go up. There will be 5 high-level spawns up there so get ready. The 5 will randomly spawn. There will be a mystical circle in front of a spinning gem. That is where the named vamp will spawn that has the Glowing Iron Pike. Problem is is that he is a random spawn, sometimes over a period of 12 hours or so, sometimes DAYS and only spawns at night. Keep in mind that while what I have stated above sounds fairly easy, MistMoore Castle is not for the faint of heart ;-). 
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
									
